item.title: Scott May stunt show Human Cannon ball tragedy
item.description:
Scott May stunt show Human Cannon ball tragedy
This is ORIGINAL footage of the Scott May human cannonball show taken in 2003. Other YouTube versions are copies of this. A stuntman performing the same act was fatally injured performing with the Scott May show on 25 April 2011 at Detling in Kent when the safety net collapsed before he landed. He was treated on site for his injuries by paramedics and the Kent Air ambulance but died shortly after. This video shows how the stunt was meant to be performed as seen at a previous show and is NOT of stuntman Matt Cranch who died at Detling.
